data.description: *SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE TO BUYER CONCESSIONS!* You do NOT want to miss this beautifully updated home in the highly desirable area of Moon Valley! Gorgeous views of Lookout Mountain from your stunning pool complete with an umbrella-shaded Baja shelf and swim-up bar, all surrounded by white travertine. Huge oversized lot, extended covered patio, artificial turf, raised flower beds, built-in BBQ, and a firepit create a perfect backyard oasis for your family and entertaining all of your guests. The kitchen was COMPLETELY remodeled and features beautiful Carrera marble countertops, subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a huge farmhouse sink, and brand new luxury cabinets. Other highlights include: dual pane windows, wood floors,  bathroom granite countertops, a kitchen pantry as well as a walk-in closet, a double door entrance to the master bedroom interior, and a wood burning fireplace. Tankless water heater added in 2022, HVAC replaced in 2022, new roof in 2021. Minutes from the Loop 101 that offers an easy drive to Desert Ridge, High Street, and The Shops at Norterra; this high demand area is close to EVERYTHING and is ready for YOU!
